{"tid":2321980,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過係公司廁所裡面同上司屙屎論英雄？","createTime":"2020-12-12T03:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T03:05:33.000Z","uid":40930,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09027340210af20385041fcb206d34ff06cf1778","tid":2321980,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:05:33.000Z","msg":"老老實實，返工屙下屎都係想個人鬆一鬆，生理需要實屬其次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知行入去屎塔，拎張廁紙擦兩擦坐低咗，就聽到你左邊個隔突然有災難式冧屎嘅聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽佢咳兩聲就知係上司，上司又聽到你啲動作聲，卒之開始同你講下職場哲學啊、人生理論咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽就肯定唔想聽㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問題係走又走唔到，又要聽你講兩句，加篤屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全同我第一句問點解要返工屙屎嘅理念背道而馳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母，屙屎都要聽你訓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跌落屎坑啦老嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：公司屙屎時請顧及他人感受，保持肅靜，多謝合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}